Projects.shortDescription: Market Price Prediction aims to address challenges in Transport using modern Machine Learning and IoT-enabled solutions.

Modules.Description: This module is responsible for gathering transport and market-related data from IoT devices and external APIs for Market Price Prediction.
This module is responsible for implementing predictive models using Machine Learning and TensorFlow for accurate market price forecasting.
This module is responsible for exposing APIs to serve prediction results and manage transport-related data.
This module provides an analytics dashboard for visualizing predictions, trends, and transport market insights.

Projects.shortDescription: AI Fraud Detection focuses on improving Transport sector security by detecting fraudulent activities using advanced Machine Learning techniques.

Modules.Description: This module collects real-time data from IoT-enabled transport systems for fraud detection.
This module leverages Machine Learning and TensorFlow models to detect unusual or fraudulent patterns in transport data.
This module is responsible for handling fraud alerts, storing incident logs, and integrating with external transport systems.
This module provides real-time monitoring and visualization of fraud detection insights for administrators and stakeholders.
